sequenceDiagram
    participant MD as Market Data
    participant MSE as Layer 1<br/>MSE
    participant ADE as Layer 2<br/>ADE
    participant ARI as Layer 3<br/>ARI
    participant TVL as Layer 4<br/>TVL
    participant PINE as TradingView<br/>Pine Strategy
    participant WH as Webhook<br/>Receiver
    participant TP as TradersPost
    participant TV as Tradovate
    participant OBS as Observatory

    Note over MD,OBS: Atlas End-to-End Production Flow v2.2 — Every 5-minute bar close

    MD->>MSE: OHLCV + transactions
    activate MSE
    MSE->>MSE: Compute 56-field Market State Object
    MSE-->>OBS: MARKET_STATE_SNAPSHOT
    MSE->>ADE: Market State Object (immutable)
    deactivate MSE

    activate ADE
    Note over ADE: Parallel evaluation of A1, A3, B1
    ADE->>ADE: Compute Edge Scores (C1–C7)
    ADE->>ADE: Rank eligible models (threshold ≥ 60)
    ADE-->>OBS: ADE_EVALUATION record

    alt No model eligible
        ADE-->>OBS: NO_TRADE record
        Note over ADE: Atlas does not trade
    else Candidate Model selected
        ADE->>ARI: Candidate Model + Edge Score
        deactivate ADE

        activate ARI
        ARI->>ARI: R1: Active position block
        ARI->>ARI: R2: Circuit breaker
        ARI->>ARI: R3: Daily loss limit
        ARI->>ARI: R4: Consecutive loss caution
        ARI->>ARI: R5: Daily trade limit
        ARI->>ARI: R6: Drawdown reduction
        ARI->>ARI: R7: Profit compounding
        ARI->>ARI: R8: Session end block
        ARI->>ARI: Calculate contracts + risk multiplier
        ARI-->>OBS: ARI_DECISION record

        alt ARI Rejects
            ARI-->>OBS: MISSED_OPPORTUNITY record
        else ARI Approves
            ARI->>TVL: Approved trade parameters
            deactivate ARI

            activate TVL
            Note over TVL: 6-Category Independent Verification

            TVL->>TVL: C1: Execution Model Verification
            Note right of TVL: Valid ID · Promoted · Eligible<br/>ADE-selected · Edge Score ≥ 60

            TVL->>TVL: C2: Market State Verification
            Note right of TVL: barstate.isrealtime · Session valid<br/>Regime unchanged · Window open<br/>MSO integrity · Price reasonable

            TVL->>TVL: C3: ARI Re-Verification
            Note right of TVL: Daily loss · Consecutive losses<br/>Circuit breaker · Trade count<br/>Active position · Risk multiplier

            TVL->>TVL: C4: Trade Parameter Verification
            Note right of TVL: Entry/Stop/Target valid<br/>Risk pts consistent · Contracts 1–10<br/>R:R ≥ 1.5 · Direction valid

            TVL->>TVL: C5: Duplicate Prevention
            Note right of TVL: Unique signal_id · Bar not traded<br/>No pending webhook · No pending order<br/>No duplicate payload · Position reconciled

            TVL->>TVL: C6: Broker Safety
            Note right of TVL: Session open · Symbol matches<br/>Account active · Broker connected<br/>Payload valid · Schema valid

            TVL-->>OBS: TVL_VERIFICATION record

            alt TVL → EMERGENCY BLOCK
                TVL-->>OBS: EMERGENCY_BLOCK record
                Note over TVL: All trading halted — manual review required
            else TVL → REJECTED
                TVL-->>OBS: TVL_REJECTED record (with rejection codes)
                Note over TVL: Webhook suppressed
            else TVL → DELAYED
                TVL-->>OBS: TVL_DELAYED record
                Note over TVL: Retry on next bar close
            else TVL → VERIFIED
                TVL->>PINE: VERIFIED — transmit alert
                deactivate TVL

                activate PINE
                PINE->>PINE: Confirm barstate.isrealtime
                PINE->>PINE: Attach signal_id to JSON payload
                PINE->>WH: HTTP POST (webhook payload)
                deactivate PINE

                activate WH
                WH->>WH: Validate JSON schema (C6-05, C6-06)
                WH->>WH: Check signal_id cache (C5-01)
                WH->>WH: Check payload hash cache (C5-05)
                WH->>WH: Verify symbol (C6-02)
                WH->>WH: Check pending webhook flag (C5-03)
                WH->>TP: Validated trade instruction
                deactivate WH

                activate TP
                TP->>TP: Check account status (C6-03)
                TP->>TP: Check broker connection (C6-04)
                TP->>TP: Check pending orders (C5-04)
                TP->>TP: Check session open (C6-01)
                TP->>TV: Order (Prop Acct 1)
                TP->>TV: Order (Prop Acct 2)
                TP->>TV: Order (Live Account)
                deactivate TP

                activate TV
                TV->>TV: Execute market order
                TV-->>OBS: TRADE_ENTRY record
                deactivate TV

                Note over TV,OBS: Trade is live — monitoring begins

                TV-->>ARI: Trade outcome (P&L)
                ARI->>ARI: Update state (consec_losses, daily_pnl, equity_peak)
                TV-->>OBS: TRADE_EXIT record
            end
        end
    end

    OBS-->>OBS: Retain all records (immutable, permanent)
    Note over OBS: Read-only — never modifies production behaviour
